Subject: Re: [PATCH 1/5] stack overflow safe kdump (2.6.15-i386) - safe_smp_processor_id
Sender: linux-kernel-owner@vger.kernel.org
Precedence: bulk
List-ID: <linux-kernel.vger.kernel.org>
